Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York car parking ban
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407hpy
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Jun 1977
Daytime car parking ban bids to ease pollution in midtown New York. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.